Package org.aion.avm.userlib.abi

Class ABIDecoder

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.aion.avm.userlib.abi.ABIDecoder
  • public class ABIDecoder
extends java.lang.Object
    Utility class for AVM ABI decoding. This class contains static methods for parsing transaction data and invoking corresponding methods.
